# Needs Engine strict quality loop (Round 3)

When iterating on prescription quality, follow [docs/NEEDS_ENGINE_QUALITY_LOOP.md](../../docs/NEEDS_ENGINE_QUALITY_LOOP.md).

## Mandatory workflow

1. Run all unit tests listed in the loop doc (including `prescriptionQualityChecks.test.js`).
2. Run `node scripts/evaluate-prescription-quality.mjs` (strict tier default) with `DATABASE_URL`.
3. Fix failures: **P0 → progression_reuse → progression_lane → stretch/youth → fill → warnings**.
4. Re-run until strict evaluator exits 0.
5. Commit and push without asking when tests + strict evaluator pass.
6. Append `strict | PASS|FAIL` line to [docs/NEEDS_ENGINE_QUALITY_LOOP.log](../../docs/NEEDS_ENGINE_QUALITY_LOOP.log).
7. Stop only when **five consecutive strict PASS** log lines exist; set Status COMPLETE.

Baseline tier (`--tier=baseline`) is a smoke check only — loop completion requires strict.
